languages.text: « Votre procession triomphale illuminera toute la Voie supérieure ! Lorsque vous voudrez commencer, adressez-vous au maître des cérémonies sur la place, Votre Seigneurie. »

languages.text: “您的胜利游行将会为整条上层街道带来光明！等您准备好之后，就和广场上的祭仪大师谈谈吧，大人。”
languages.original_text: "Your triumphal procession will illuminate the entire Upperway! When you are ready to begin, speak to the Master of Ceremonies in the square, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}."

traits.locale_text: “您的胜利游行将会为整条流星大道带来光明！等您准备好之后，就和广场上的祭仪大师谈谈吧，大人。”

languages.text: 「あなた様の勝利の行進が、上通り全体を照らすことでしょう！準備がおできになったら、広場にいる式典のマスターにお声がけください、陛下」
languages.original_text: "Your triumphal procession will illuminate the entire Upperway! When you are ready to begin, speak to the Master of Ceremonies in the square, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}."

languages.text: «¡Su procesión triunfal será el centro de atención de toda la Vía Superior! Cuando esté {mf|listo|lista} para comenzar, hable con el maestro de ceremonias que se encuentra en la plaza, {mf|milord|milady}».
languages.original_text: "Your triumphal procession will illuminate the entire Upperway! When you are ready to begin, speak to the Master of Ceremonies in the square, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}."
